{"tid":2306451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"近九成紀律部隊人員申請延遲退休 警務處人數最多但比率最低","createTime":"2020-11-30T12:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T13:18:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b55fdd4d38b7e7cc84cc5f32a00cbfb25bfbd6c0","tid":2306451,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"政府在2018年向現職公務員推出自願選擇延遲退休方案，兩年選擇期今年9月中結束，共有83%合資格公務員，即4.7萬人申請延遲退休，可多做5年。公務員事務局數字顯示，紀律部隊有近九成合資格人員申請延遲退休，雖然警隊有多達9,114人申請延遲退休，申請人數是紀律部隊中最多，但佔合資格申請者比率卻只有85%，是紀律部隊中最低。<br />\n<br />\n六大紀律部隊中，以海關人員申請延遲退休的比率最多，有1,696人申請延遲退休，比率高達95%。其餘依次分別是政府飛行服務隊、消防處、入境事務處及懲教署，分別有53人、3,670人、2,247人及1,868人申請延遲退休，佔合資格申請者比率93%、93%、92%及91%。<br />\n<br />\n警務處有10,714人合資格申請延遲退休，但只有9,114人提出申請，比率約85%，在六大紀律部隊中包尾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201130/REPCE4LHPRCFVPORIV7REYZB6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201130%2FREPCE4LHPRCFVPORIV7REYZB6U%2F&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=345ae743\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201130%2FREPCE4LHPRCFVPORIV7REYZB6U%2F&h=4d7d96aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201130/REPCE4LHPRCFVPORIV7REYZB6U/</a>"},{"pid":"9400026e58bdbb4899269e829f751c44a57e0b4b","tid":2306451,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416c4bb929b22f186664e3d626eb37d12edd485f","tid":2306451,"uid":183844,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:25:37.000Z","msg":"所以仲係狗嘅無一隻無辜"},{"pid":"44b03928ef28f0006b61d67973a0c25428ad0bd5","tid":2306451,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im